description: This dashboard shows live load test metrics provided by JMeter.

panels.content: The following panels show aggregated metrics for all requests

targets.query: SELECT  count("response_time")/$aggregation FROM "vugen_stats" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)
SELECT count("response_time") FROM "vugen_stats"  WHERE $timeFilter
SELECT "finishedThreads" FROM "virtualUsers" WHERE $timeFilter
SELECT count("Status") FROM "vugen_stats" WHERE ("Status" = 'Fail') AND $timeFilter
SELECT mean("response_time") FROM "autogen"."vugen_stats" WHERE ("Status" = 'Pass') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), "transaction_name"
SELECT  count("Status")/$aggregation FROM "vugen_stats" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)
SELECT  count("response_time")/$aggregation FROM "vugen_stats" WHERE "transaction_name" =~ /CM/ and $timeFilter GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)
SELECT mean("response_time") FROM "autogen"."vugen_stats" WHERE ("Status" = 'Pass') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), "transaction_name"
SELECT  count("response_time")/$aggregation FROM "vugen_stats" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)
SELECT  count("response_time")/$aggregation FROM "vugen_stats" WHERE "transaction_name" =~ /RPL/ and $timeFilter GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)

SELECT count(PassCount) as Pass,count(FailCount) as Fail, (count(PassCount)/(count(PassCount)+count(FailCount))*100) as "% Passed", mean(PassCount) as Avg, min(PassCount) as Min, percentile(PassCount, 90) as "90%", max(PassCount) as Max from 
(
select "response_time" as "PassCount" from "vugen_stats" where "Status" = 'Pass'  and $timeFilter),
(
select "Status" as "FailCount" from "vugen_stats" where "Status" = 'Fail' and $timeFilter
)
group by transaction_name fill(0)

SELECT "Status" Pass/(Pass+Fail) * 100 AS "Pass", "response_time" AS "Avg", "response_time" AS "90%", "response_time" AS "Min", "response_time" AS "Max" FROM "vugen_stats" WHERE ("Status" = 'Pass') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "transaction_name"

select count("Status") as Fail from "vugen_stats" where "Status"='Fail' as F inner join select count("Status") as Pass from "vugen_stats" where "Status"='Pass' as P  where F.transaction_name = P.transaction_name

SELECT count("Status") AS "Fail", count(response_time) as Pass,mean(response_time) as Avg, min(response_time) as Min, percentile(response_time, 90) as "90%", max(response_time) as Max  FROM (SELECT status  FROM "vugen_stats" where "Status" = 'Fail')  , (SELECT * FROM "vugen_stats" where "Status" = 'Pass')   GROUP BY "transaction_name" fill(null)

SELECT count(response_time) as Pass,mean(response_time) as Avg, min(response_time) as Min, percentile(response_time, 90) as "90%", max(response_time) as Max  FROM "vugen_stats"  WHERE $timeFilter and "Status" = 'Pass' GROUP BY transaction_name
select count("Status") as Fail from "vugen_stats" where "Status" = 'Fail' and $timeFilter group by transaction_name
select count(Status) as Pass, count(Fail) as Fail from "vugen_stats","vugen_fail" where $timeFilter group by transaction_name

SELECT count(abcd) as Pass,count(failed) as Fail, mean(abcd) as Avg, min(abcd) as Min, percentile(abcd, 90) as "90%", max(abcd) as Max from 
(
select "response_time" as "abcd" from "vugen_stats" where $timeFilter and "Status" = 'Pass'),
(
select "Status" as failed from "vugen_stats" where $timeFilter and "Status" = 'Fail'
)
group by transaction_name
select count(Data) as ErrCount from vugen_err where $timeFilter  group by  Transaction_name,ErrDesc
select Data from vugen_err where $timeFilter and Transaction_name =~ /ICCID/ group by  Transaction_name,ErrDesc

panels.content: The following panels show request-specific metrics for the request "[[request]]"

targets.query: select count(Data) as ErrCount from vugen_err where ErrDesc !~ /Concurrent/ and  $timeFilter GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)
SELECT count("Status") FROM "vugen_stats" WHERE  "Status" = 'Fail' AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)
SELECT count("Status") FROM "vugen_stats" WHERE  "transaction_name" =~ /CM/ and "Status" = 'Fail' AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)
SELECT count("Status") FROM "vugen_stats" WHERE  "transaction_name" =~ /RPL/ and "Status" = 'Fail' AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)
SELECT count("Status") FROM "vugen_stats" WHERE  "transaction_name" =~ /de_ISO/ and "Status" = 'Fail' AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)
SELECT count("response_time")/$aggregation FROM "vugen_stats" WHERE "transaction_name" =~ /^$request$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)
SELECT count("Status") FROM "vugen_stats" WHERE ("Status" = 'Pass' AND "transaction_name" =~ /^$request$/) AND $timeFilter
SELECT count("Status") FROM "vugen_stats" WHERE  "Status" = 'Pass' AND $timeFilter
SELECT count("responseTime") FROM "requestsRaw" WHERE ("requestName" =~ /^$request$/) AND $timeFilter
SELECT count("Status") FROM "vugen_stats" WHERE ("Status" = 'Fail' AND "transaction_name" =~ /de_ISO/) AND $timeFilter
SELECT count("Status") FROM "vugen_stats" WHERE  "Status" = 'Fail' AND $timeFilter
select count(Data) from vugen_err where ErrDesc !~ /Concurrent/  and $timeFilter
select count(Data) from vugen_err where ErrDesc !~ /Concurrent/ and Transaction_name =~ /CM/ and $timeFilter
SELECT mean("response_time") FROM "vugen_stats" WHERE "transaction_name" =~ /^$request$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)
SELECT percentile("response_time", 90) FROM "vugen_stats" WHERE "transaction_name" =~ /^$request$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)
SELECT percentile("response_time", 95) FROM "vugen_stats" WHERE "transaction_name" =~ /^$request$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)
SELECT percentile("response_time", 99) FROM "vugen_stats" WHERE "transaction_name" =~ /^$request$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)
SELECT max("response_time") FROM "vugen_stats" WHERE "transaction_name" =~ /^$request$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)
